1. What are AFK tasks?: AFK tasks are passive sources of resources and coins which are necessary for in-game progress.
   It's a typical mechanic: You go to the AFK tasks panel, choose a job you want to do and wait. Then claim your pay when completed.

2. Job types: - Scavenging: For coins and trait imbuers from common grade to special grade with its chances (Cm: 59%, Uu: 20%, Uq 13%, Sp 8%) 
              - Thieving: For coins and tier-up sets from common grade to special grade with its chances (59,20,13,8)
              - Bodyguarding: For coins and 
            
